msg: STANBOL-990: SentiWordNet (en) and SentiWSComponent (de) now use lowercase for matching. Both the dictionary and parsed words are converted to the lower case version by using the Locale of the according dictionary.

author: rwesten
msg: minor: Improved error messages for Exceptions thorwn by the RESTful NLP Analysis Engine. In detail exceptions will now include information provided by the response entity on status codes >= 300. This will allow Stanbol users to see the original stack trace as provided by the RESTful NLP Analyses service (related to STANBOL-893)
